snippet.title: Gears POP! Boomer Buddy gamescom
snippet.description:
Brought to you by Xbox and Funko Animation Studios, “Boomer Buddy” is the second in a series of animated shorts starring the characters from Gears POP!

Audio Description: https://youtu.be/FeoyeG4JnDc
